panels.content:
Latency Patterns

This dashboard shows heatmaps for latency across links using perfSONAR active testing data.
The horizontal axis represents days and the vertical axis represents time of day.
Darker squares show longer delays in data transmissions at those hours.
The accompanying graphs show the latency over time and a histogram of the latency in milliseconds.
All times are displayed in browser local time.
